<item>
            <title>[LU-17005] allow lprocfs stats header to be disabled</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17005</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The addition of the &lt;tt&gt;start_time&lt;/tt&gt; and &lt;tt&gt;elapsed_time&lt;/tt&gt; fields in the lprocfs stats header in patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/49745&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/49745&lt;/a&gt; &quot;&lt;tt&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11407&quot; title=&quot;Improve stats data&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-11407&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-11407&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; obdclass: add start time to stats files&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; may break stats parsing if it has not been updated to understand these fields.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Add a tunable parameter &quot;&lt;tt&gt;enable_stats_header&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; to allow the header to be enabled/disabled globally.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
